Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.35,0:47:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and little pee peep. You know, pee pee\Nwould be in my hands like this and the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.68,0:47:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,little the little duckling when it was\Nborn thought I was its mother.
